(911, 'Animatrix/Animatrix 2 - The Second Renaissance Part 1.m4v', 'The Second Renaissance Part 1', 4, 17, 'en', 'cz', 'en', '', '', 'Animatrix 2 - The Second Renaissance Part 1.jpg', 5, 'Directed by Mahiro Maeda. With Dane A. Davis, Debi Derryberry, Julia Fletcher, Dwight Schultz. A tour is taken into the Zion archives, where the history of the real world and the rise of the machines is shown to viewers.', NULL),
(2272, '201309/020 Armada versus namornictvo.m4v', 'Armada versus namornictvo', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '020 Armada versus namornictvo.jpg', 20, STRINGDECODE('Major Fred C. Dobbs: Frank u\u00c5\u00be m\u00c3\u00a1 v\u00c5\u00a1eho dost a po dohod\u00c4\u009b s Margaret po\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00a1d\u00c3\u00a1 o transfer. Margaret se chce tak\u00c3\u00a9 nechat p\u00c5\u0099elo\u00c5\u00beit, kdy\u00c5\u00be n\u00c3\u00a1hle p\u00c5\u0099ijde zpr\u00c3\u00a1va, \u00c5\u00bee Hawkeye a Trapper objevili v okol\u00c3\u00ad t\u00c3\u00a1bora zlato. To rozhodne - Frank a \u00c5\u00a0\u00c5\u00a5abajzna z\u00c5\u00afst\u00c3\u00a1vaj\u00c3\u00ad a st\u00c3\u00a1vaj\u00c3\u00ad se z nich prospekto\u00c5\u0099i. Frank opravdu najde mnoho \"zlat\u00c3\u00bdch\" p\u00c5\u0099edm\u00c4\u009bt\u00c5\u00af, dokonce i zlat\u00c3\u00bd d\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00adp.'), NULL),
(2311, '201309/028 Pro dobro kolektivu.m4v', 'Pro dobro kolektivu', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '028 Pro dobro kolektivu.jpg', 28, STRINGDECODE('Pro dobro kolektivu: Hawkeye a Trapper upozorn\u00c3\u00ad na vybombardov\u00c3\u00a1n\u00c3\u00ad korejsk\u00c3\u00a9 vesnice Tai Dong Ameri\u00c4\u008dany. Ne\u00c5\u00be arm\u00c3\u00a1da p\u00c5\u0099ijme svou odpov\u00c4\u009bdnost, pl\u00c3\u00a1nuj\u00c3\u00ad p\u00c5\u0099estavbu vesnice. Arm\u00c3\u00a1da se ale pokou\u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00ad sv\u00c3\u00a9st odpov\u00c4\u009bdnost na nep\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adtele.'), NULL),
