(20000, '201406/ANGEL_HEART.m4v', 'Angel Heart', 2, 0, 'cz', NULL, 'en', 'Angel Heart', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/7109-angel-heart/', 'ANGEL_HEART.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Amerika roku 1955, jazz a m\u00edsta v autobusech vyhrazen\u00e1 jen pro b\u00edl\u00e9. Soukrom\u00e9 o\u010dko Harry Angel (Mickey Rourke) dostane neobvykl\u00fd k\u0161eft - pro podiv\u00ednsk\u00e9ho pr\u00e1vn\u00edka jm\u00e9nem Louis Cyphre vyp\u00e1trat jist\u00e9ho Johnyho Favoritea, kter\u00e9ho 12 let nikdo nevid\u011bl. Angel se vyd\u00e1v\u00e1 za stopou a m\u00edsto odpov\u011bd\u00ed nach\u00e1z\u00ed jen dal\u0161\u00ed ot\u00e1zky. Pot\u00e9, co kolem n\u011bj za\u010dnou um\u00edrat sv\u011bdkov\u00e9, Angel pochop\u00ed, \u017ee tohle nen\u00ed jen tak lecjak\u00e1 pr\u00e1ce a \u017ee mu za\u010d\u00edn\u00e1 j\u00edt o krk...(\u010cSFD.cz)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-06-23 20:56:32.238');
