(9975, '201405/S205.m4v', 'The Ghost of Harrenhal', 4, 1000, 'en', 'cz', 'en', '', '', 'S205.jpg', 205, 'The Ghost of Harrenhal: Confusion rages in the Stormlands in the wake of a devastating reversal. Catelyn must flee with a new ally, whilst Littlefinger sees an opportunity in the chaos. Theon seeks to prove himself to his father in battle. Arya receives a promise from the enigmatic Jaqen H''ghar. The Night''s Watch arrives at the Fist of the First Men. Daenerys Targaryen receives a marriage proposal.', TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:06.613'),
(2332, '201309/049 General za usvitu.m4v', 'General za usvitu', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '049 General za usvitu.jpg', 49, STRINGDECODE('Duhov\u00c3\u00bd most: Hawkeye a Traper pl\u00c3\u00a1nuj\u00c3\u00ad dovolenou v Tokiu, kdy\u00c5\u00be p\u00c5\u0099ijde nab\u00c3\u00addka na v\u00c3\u00bdm\u00c4\u009bnu americk\u00c3\u00bdch ran\u00c4\u009bn\u00c3\u00bdch za \u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00adnsk\u00c3\u00a9 zajatce a jednotka 4077 m\u00c3\u00a1 v\u00c3\u00bdm\u00c4\u009bnu prov\u00c3\u00a9st. Henry se rozhodne vyslat Hawkeyeho, Trapera, Burnse, Radara a Klingera na misi na nep\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00a1telsk\u00c3\u00a9 \u00c3\u00bazem\u00c3\u00ad. Frank m\u00c3\u00a1lem v\u00c5\u00a1echno pokaz\u00c3\u00ad, kdy\u00c5\u00be si p\u00c5\u0099es striktn\u00c3\u00ad p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adkaz vezme st\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adkac\u00c3\u00ad pistolku. Na\u00c5\u00a1t\u00c4\u009bst\u00c3\u00ad \u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00adnsk\u00c3\u00bd doktor projev\u00c3\u00ad dostatek smyslu pro humor - asi proto, \u00c5\u00bee studoval na univerzit\u00c4\u009b v Illinois.'), NULL),
