(936, 'Detske/Karlik a tovaren na cokoladu -- Charlie and The Chocolate Factory.m4v', 'Karlik a tovaren na cokoladu', 3, NULL, 'cz', '  ', 'en', 'Charlie and The Chocolate Factory', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/135983-karlik-a-tovarna-na-cokoladu/', 'Karlik a tovaren na cokoladu -- Charlie and The Chocolate Factory.jpg', 80, STRINGDECODE('Charlie Bucket je mal\u00fd chlapec, poch\u00e1dzaj\u00faci z celkom zbeda\u010denej rodiny, b\u00fdva na okraji mesta hne\u010f ved\u013ea obrovskej tov\u00e1rne na \u010dokol\u00e1du. Charlie miluje \u010dokol\u00e1du, aj ke\u010f dost\u00e1va \u010dokol\u00e1dov\u00fd bomb\u00f3n len raz do roka. Jedn\u00e9ho d\u0148a v\u0161ak vyhr\u00e1 aj s \u010fal\u0161\u00edmi \u0161tyrmi de\u0165mi cestu po fantastickej \u010dokol\u00e1dovej tov\u00e1rni, ktor\u00fa vlastn\u00ed excentrick\u00fd Willy Wonka a jeho nemenej zauj\u00edmav\u00ed zamestnanci.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(937, 'Detske/Kniha dzungli.m4v', 'Kniha dzungli', 3, NULL, 'cz', '  ', 'en', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/277253-kniha-dzungli-maugliho-dobrodruzstvi/', 'Kniha dzungli.jpg', 27, STRINGDECODE('Sv\u011btozn\u00e1m\u00fd rom\u00e1n Rudyarda Kiplinga je p\u0159\u00edb\u011bhem mal\u00e9ho chlapce Maugl\u00edho, kter\u00fd se ztratil v d\u017eungli a byl adoptov\u00e1n rodinou vlk\u016f. Neust\u00e1le pron\u00e1sledov\u00e1n zl\u00fdm beng\u00e1lsk\u00fdm tygrem \u0160\u00e9r Ch\u00e1nem, pro\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 Maugl\u00ed sv\u00e1 dobrodru\u017estv\u00ed spole\u010dn\u011b se svoj\u00ed vl\u010d\u00ed rodinou pod ochranou \u010dern\u00e9ho pantera Bagh\u00edry a moudr\u00e9ho medv\u011bda Bal\u00faa, kter\u00fd u\u010d\u00ed z\u00e1kon\u016fm d\u017eungle nejen chlapce, ale i celou jeho vl\u010d\u00ed sme\u010dku.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(938, 'Detske/Lisiacik Vuk.m4v', 'Lisiacik Vuk', 3, NULL, 'sk', '  ', 'en', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/94781-lisacek-lup/', 'Lisiacik Vuk.jpg', 26, STRINGDECODE('Mal\u00fd li\u0161\u00e1\u010dek Vuk je velk\u00fd nezbedn\u00edk. Nen\u00ed v\u0161ak s\u00e1m, v probl\u00e9mech mu pom\u00e1h\u00e1 v\u011brn\u00fd kamar\u00e1d Karak. Dohromady mus\u00ed \u010delit velk\u00e9mu nebezpe\u010d\u00ed v podob\u011b zl\u00e9ho lovce. Poda\u0159\u00ed se jim to? Mus\u00ed zachr\u00e1nit p\u0159\u00edtelkyni li\u0161ku a za\u017eij\u00ed p\u0159i tom i mnoho vesel\u00fdch dobrodru\u017estv\u00ed a p\u0159\u00edhod.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
