(1091, 'James Bond/1983 James Bond - Chobotnicka -- Octopussy.m4v', 'Chobotnicka', 15, 15, 'cz', '  ', 'en', 'Octopussy', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0086034/', '1983 James Bond - Chobotnicka -- Octopussy.jpg', 13, STRINGDECODE('Directed by John Glen.  With Roger Moore, Maud Adams, Louis Jourdan, Kristina Wayborn. A fake Faberg\u00e9 egg and a fellow agent''s death lead James Bond to uncover an international jewel-smuggling operation, headed by the mysterious Octopussy, being used to disguise a nuclear attack on N.A.T.O. forces.'), NULL),
