(1079, 'James Bond/1962 James Bond - Dr.m4v', '1962 Doktor No', 15, 15, 'cz', '  ', 'en', 'Dr. No', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0055928/', '1962 James Bond - Dr.jpg', 1, 'Directed by Terence Young. With Sean Connery, Ursula Andress, Bernard Lee, Joseph Wiseman. James Bond&#x27;s investigation of a missing colleague in Jamaica leads him to the island of the mysterious Dr. No and a scheme to end the US space program.', NULL),
