(1090, 'James Bond/1981 James Bond - Len pre tvoje oci -- For Your Eyes Only.m4v', 'Len pre tvoje oci', 15, 15, 'cz', '  ', 'en', 'For Your Eyes Only', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0082398/', '1981 James Bond - Len pre tvoje oci -- For Your Eyes Only.jpg', 12, 'Directed by John Glen. With Roger Moore, Carole Bouquet, Topol, Lynn-Holly Johnson. Agent 007 is assigned to hunt for a lost British encryption device and prevent it from falling into enemy hands.', NULL),
