(2294, '201309/083 O parohacich a lidech.m4v', 'O parohacich a lidech', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '083 O parohacich a lidech.jpg', 83, STRINGDECODE('D\u00c4\u009bti: Jednotka 4077 host\u00c3\u00ad n\u00c4\u009bkolik dn\u00c5\u00af sirotky, kte\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad se mus\u00c3\u00ad ukr\u00c3\u00bdt p\u00c5\u0099ed bombardov\u00c3\u00a1n\u00c3\u00adm. Ve stejn\u00c3\u00a9 dob\u00c4\u009b zachr\u00c3\u00a1n\u00c3\u00ad \u00c5\u00beivot post\u00c5\u0099elen\u00c3\u00a9 t\u00c4\u009bhotn\u00c3\u00a9 \u00c5\u00beene i jej\u00c3\u00admu d\u00c3\u00adt\u00c4\u009bti, kter\u00c3\u00a9mu nav\u00c3\u00adc ud\u00c4\u009bl\u00c3\u00ad \u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00a1d purpurov\u00c3\u00a9ho srdce.'), NULL),
(2330, '201309/047 Posta vola.m4v', 'Posta vola', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '047 Posta vola.jpg', 47, STRINGDECODE('Po\u00c5\u00a1ta vol\u00c3\u00a1: Dopis z domova vyvol\u00c3\u00a1 v Traperovi depresi a touhu - rozhodne se dezertovat, p\u00c5\u0099esto\u00c5\u00bee se mu v tom Hawkeye sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad zabr\u00c3\u00a1nit. Mezit\u00c3\u00adm se Hawkeymu poda\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad \u00c3\u00basp\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u00a1n\u00c4\u009b nap\u00c3\u00a1lit Franka - p\u00c5\u0099emluv\u00c3\u00ad jej, aby koupil akcie fiktivn\u00c3\u00ad spole\u00c4\u008dnosti - Pioneer Aviation.'), NULL),
(33210, '201411/SCOOBYDOO_WRESTLEMANIA_MYSTERY.m4v', 'Scooby Doo zahada kolem Wrestlemanie', 3, 30010, 'cz', NULL, 'en', 'Scooby Doo WrestleMania Mystery', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/366273-scooby-doo-zahada-kolem-wrestlemanie/', 'SCOOBYDOO_WRESTLEMANIA_MYSTERY.jpg', 1, STRINGDECODE('P\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed zbrusu nov\u00fd p\u016fvodn\u00ed film a s n\u00edm ne\u00fanavn\u011b ak\u010dn\u00ed Scooby - Doo, Shaggy a dal\u0161\u00ed \u010dlenov\u00e9 jejich gangu! Z\u00e1hada za\u010d\u00edn\u00e1, kdy\u017e Shaggy a Scooby - Doo vyhraj\u00ed l\u00edstky na s\u00e9rii z\u00e1pas\u016f do WWE City a p\u0159esv\u011bd\u010d\u00ed ostatn\u00ed, aby se k nim p\u0159idali. Jen\u017ee tohle m\u011bsto skr\u00fdv\u00e1 stra\u0161n\u00e9 tajemstv\u00ed: drtivou silou je sv\u00edr\u00e1 Medv\u011bd\u00ed p\u0159\u00edzrak! Zachr\u00e1nit vytou\u017een\u00fd titul pomohou na\u0161im kamar\u00e1d\u016fm i superhv\u011bzdy jako John Cena, Triple H, Sin Cara, Brodus Clay, AJ Lee, The Miz a Kane. Sledujte Scooby - Dooa a jeho partu, jak se sna\u017e\u00ed p\u0159ij\u00edt cel\u00e9 v\u011bci na kloub d\u0159\u00edv, ne\u017e bude pozd\u011b. Skv\u011bl\u00e9 dobrodru\u017estv\u00ed pro celou rodinu - to mus\u00edte m\u00edt je\u0161t\u011b dnes!(Magic Box)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-11-23 19:51:35.646'),
(2277, '201309/050 Domaci vezeni.m4v', 'Domaci vezeni', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '050 Domaci vezeni.jpg', 50, STRINGDECODE('\u00c5\u00bdivot s Otcem: Velitel Henry dostane z domova dopis, ze kter\u00c3\u00a9ho si vydedukuje, \u00c5\u00bee jeho \u00c5\u00beena m\u00c3\u00a1 mo\u00c5\u00ben\u00c3\u00a1 jin\u00c3\u00a9ho mu\u00c5\u00bee. Otec Mulcahy provede \u00c5\u00beidovsk\u00c3\u00bd ob\u00c5\u0099ad k\u00c5\u0099tu pro korejsk\u00c3\u00a9 d\u00c3\u00adt\u00c4\u009b americk\u00c3\u00a9ho voj\u00c3\u00a1ka.'), NULL),
(33220, '201411/MALEFICENT.m4v', 'Vladkyna zla', 3, 0, 'sk', NULL, 'en', 'Maleficent', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/210164-zloba-kralovna-cerne-magie/', 'MALEFICENT.jpg', 1, STRINGDECODE('Sn\u00edmek Zloba \u2013 Kr\u00e1lovna \u010dern\u00e9 magie vypr\u00e1v\u00ed dosud nezpracovan\u00fd p\u0159\u00edb\u011bh legend\u00e1rn\u00ed zl\u00e9 kr\u00e1lovny z klasick\u00e9ho sn\u00edmku spole\u010dnosti Disney \u0160\u00edpkov\u00e1 R\u016f\u017eenka z roku 1959, a seznamuje div\u00e1ky s jej\u00ed zradou, kter\u00e1 nakonec zp\u016fsobila, \u017ee se jej\u00ed kdysi \u010dist\u00e9 srdce prom\u011bnilo v k\u00e1men. Kr\u00e1lovna Zloba, hnan\u00e1 touhou po pomst\u011b a urputnou snahou udr\u017eet si tr\u016fn, uvrhne na novorozenou dcerku lidsk\u00e9ho kr\u00e1le, Auroru, krutou kletbu. Jak princezna roste, ocit\u00e1 se p\u0159\u00edmo v sam\u00e9m st\u0159edu nar\u016fstaj\u00edc\u00edho konfliktu mezi lesn\u00edm kr\u00e1lovstv\u00edm, kter\u00e9 si zamilovala, a lidsk\u00fdm kr\u00e1lovstv\u00edm, ze kter\u00e9ho poch\u00e1z\u00ed. Zloba si uv\u011bdomuje, \u017ee princezna m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt kl\u00ed\u010dem k m\u00edru mezi ob\u011bma \u0159\u00ed\u0161emi a je tak nucena k nemilosrdn\u00fdm \u010din\u016fm, kter\u00e9 oba sv\u011bty nav\u017edy zm\u011bn\u00ed.(Falcon)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-11-23 19:51:35.837');
