(9965, '201405/S105.m4v', 'The Wolf and the Lion', 4, 1000, 'cz', 'cz', 'en', '', '', 'S105.jpg', 105, 'The Wolf and the Lion: Tyrion''s predicament becomes common knowledge in King''s Landing, making life difficult for Eddard Stark. Ned''s position is already precarious due to a disagreement with King Robert Baratheon over plans to assassinate Daenerys before she can rally the Dothraki to invade Westeros. In the Eyrie, Catelyn is shocked by her sister Lysa''s paranoia and distrust.', TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:05.869'),
(9961, '201405/S101.m4v', 'Winter Is Coming', 4, 1000, 'cz', 'cz', 'en', '', '', 'S101.jpg', 101, 'Winter Is Coming: King Robert Baratheon majestically arrives in Winterfell, the home of his old and trusted friend, Eddard Stark, Warden of the North, with an important offer. On the eastern continent, the dispossessed Princess Daenerys Targaryen marries Khal Drogo, a warlord of the Dothraki with tens of thousands of warriors at his command. Her brother, Viserys, callously plans to win Drogo''s allegiance with the marriage, so that he may return home to Westeros and reclaim the Iron Throne, which was seized by force from his father by Robert. In the frozen lands, beyond the Wall, the wildlings are on the move to the alarm of the Night''s Watch. But something else is stirring even further north.', TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:05.583'),
(2274, '201309/022 Major Fred C Dobbs.m4v', 'Major Fred C Dobbs', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '022 Major Fred C Dobbs.jpg', 22, STRINGDECODE('Arm\u00c3\u00a1da versus N\u00c3\u00a1mo\u00c5\u0099nictvo: V pr\u00c5\u00afb\u00c4\u009bhu tradi\u00c4\u008dn\u00c3\u00adho z\u00c3\u00a1pasu arm\u00c3\u00a1da versus n\u00c3\u00a1mo\u00c5\u0099nictvo v americk\u00c3\u00a9m fotbalu, kter\u00c3\u00bd v\u00c5\u00a1ichni sleduj\u00c3\u00ad v r\u00c3\u00a1diu, je t\u00c3\u00a1bor ost\u00c5\u0099elov\u00c3\u00a1n a jedna nevybuchl\u00c3\u00a1 bomba z\u00c5\u00afstane le\u00c5\u00beet uprost\u00c5\u0099ed t\u00c3\u00a1bora. Kdy\u00c5\u00be se ji Hawkeye a Trapper pokou\u00c5\u00a1ej\u00c3\u00ad zne\u00c5\u00a1kodnit, vybuchne a vylet\u00c3\u00ad z n\u00c3\u00ad americk\u00c3\u00a9 propaga\u00c4\u008dn\u00c3\u00ad let\u00c3\u00a1ky.'), NULL),
(2331, '201309/048 Souboj agentu.m4v', 'Souboj agentu', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '048 Souboj agentu.jpg', 48, STRINGDECODE('Souboj agent\u00c5\u00af: Pomaten\u00c3\u00bd plukovn\u00c3\u00adk Flagg a jin\u00c3\u00bd tajn\u00c3\u00bd agent z jin\u00c3\u00a9 zpravodajsk\u00c3\u00a9 slu\u00c5\u00beby se vydaj\u00c3\u00ad do t\u00c3\u00a1bora, aby tajn\u00c4\u009b sledovali jeden druh\u00c3\u00a9ho. Hawkeye a Traper zp\u00c5\u00afsob\u00c3\u00ad, \u00c5\u00bee si oba agenti mysl\u00c3\u00ad, ze Frank Burns je zr\u00c3\u00a1dce - jeden ho pova\u00c5\u00beuje za fa\u00c5\u00a1istu a druh\u00c3\u00bd za komunistu.'), NULL),
