(9960, '201405/OBLIVION.m4v', 'Nevedomi', 4, 0, 'cz', 'cz', 'en', 'Oblivion', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/282846-nevedomi/', 'OBLIVION.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Jacka (Tom Cruise), kter\u00e9ho na Zemi bav\u00ed p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm hled\u00e1n\u00ed artefakt\u016f zanikaj\u00edc\u00ed lidsk\u00e9 civilizace, vyvedou z ka\u017edodenn\u00ed rutiny dv\u011b ud\u00e1losti. Tou prvn\u00ed je nouzov\u00e9 p\u0159ist\u00e1n\u00ed vesm\u00edrn\u00e9 lodi, jej\u00ed\u017e jedin\u00e1 \u010dlenka pos\u00e1dky (Olga Kurylenko) tvrd\u00ed, \u017ee ji s Jackem poj\u00ed spole\u010dn\u00e1 minulost, ani\u017e pro to existuje racion\u00e1ln\u00ed vysv\u011btlen\u00ed. N\u00e1sledn\u011b je Jack zajat ileg\u00e1ln\u00ed arm\u00e1dou operuj\u00edc\u00ed pod zemsk\u00fdm povrchem, jej\u00ed\u017e charismatick\u00fd v\u016fdce Beech (Morgan Freeman) toho o n\u011bm v\u00ed v\u00edc ne\u017e on s\u00e1m. Pod vlivem t\u011bchto ud\u00e1lost\u00ed se Jack rozhodne pod\u00edvat na sv\u011bt kolem sebe jin\u00fdma o\u010dima a z toho, co uvid\u00ed, mu nen\u00ed dvakr\u00e1t dob\u0159e\u2026(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:05.514'),
(9991, '201405/UP.m4v', 'Hore', 3, 0, 'cz', 'cz', 'en', 'Up', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/236791-vzhuru-do-oblak/', 'UP.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Vzh\u016fru do oblak je p\u0159\u00edb\u011bh o 78let\u00e9m prodejci bal\u00f3nk\u016f Carlovi Fredricksenovi, kter\u00fd si kone\u010dn\u011b spln\u00ed celo\u017eivotn\u00ed sen o dobrodru\u017estv\u00edch, kdy\u017e na sv\u016fj domek p\u0159iv\u00e1\u017ee tis\u00edce bal\u00f3nk\u016f a odlet\u00ed s n\u00edm do divo\u010diny Ji\u017en\u00ed Ameriky. A\u017e p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 pozd\u011b ale zjist\u00ed, \u017ee se k n\u011bmu potaj\u00ed p\u0159ipojil i p\u016fvodce jeho nejhor\u0161\u00edch no\u010dn\u00edch m\u016fr: nad\u0161en\u00fd osmilet\u00fd pr\u016fzkumn\u00edk divo\u010diny jm\u00e9nem Russell. Jejich spole\u010dn\u00e1 pou\u0165 do ztracen\u00e9ho sv\u011bta, v n\u011bm\u017e se setk\u00e1vaj\u00ed s v\u0161emo\u017en\u00fdmi zvl\u00e1\u0161tn\u00edmi, exotick\u00fdmi a p\u0159ekvapiv\u00fdmi postavami, je pln\u00e1 humoru, emoc\u00ed a obrovsky n\u00e1padit\u00fdch p\u0159\u00edhod. Sou\u010dasn\u011b se jedn\u00e1 o v\u00fdro\u010dn\u00ed des\u00e1t\u00fd film studia Pixar.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:07.754'),
(2298, '201309/087 Cena tomatoveho dzusu.m4v', 'Cena tomatoveho dzusu', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '087 Cena tomatoveho dzusu.jpg', 87, STRINGDECODE('Drah\u00c3\u00a1 mami: Radar p\u00c3\u00ad\u00c5\u00a1e dopis dom\u00c5\u00af sv\u00c3\u00a9 matce o \u00c5\u00beivot\u00c4\u009b v jednotce. Popisuje Hawkeyho celot\u00c3\u00a1borovou inspekci nohou a tak\u00c3\u00a9 zran\u00c4\u009bn\u00c3\u00ad plukovn\u00c3\u00adka Pottera, kter\u00c3\u00bd je post\u00c5\u0099elen do zadku.'), NULL),
(21027, '201407/FRANKENWEENIE.m4v', 'Frankenweenie', 3, 0, 'en', 'cz', 'en', 'Frankenweenie', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/236117-frankenweenie-domaci-mazlicek/', 'FRANKENWEENIE.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Frankenweenie: Dom\u00e1c\u00ed mazl\u00ed\u010dek je dojemn\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edb\u011bhem chlapce a jeho psa. Kdy\u017e mlad\u00fd Victor ne\u010dekan\u011b p\u0159ijde o sv\u00e9ho milovan\u00e9ho psa Sparkyho, povol\u00e1 na pomoc v\u011bdu a sv\u00e9ho nejlep\u0161\u00edho p\u0159\u00edtele p\u0159ivede znovu k \u017eivotu \u2013 jen s n\u011bkolika drobn\u00fdmi zm\u011bnami. Sna\u017e\u00ed se sv\u016fj v\u00fdtvor ukr\u00fdvat, ale kdy\u017e se Sparkymu poda\u0159\u00ed uniknout, zjist\u00ed Victorovi spolu\u017e\u00e1ci, u\u010ditel\u00e9 i ostatn\u00ed obyvatel\u00e9 m\u011bsta, \u017ee znovuzrozen\u00ed m\u016f\u017ee m\u00edt p\u0159\u00ed\u0161ern\u00e9 n\u00e1sledky.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-07-24 03:10:12.308');
