(2321, '201309/038 Stabajzna a prazdna naruc.m4v', 'Stabajzna a prazdna naruc', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '038 Stabajzna a prazdna naruc.jpg', 38, STRINGDECODE('\u00c5\u00a0\u00c5\u00a5abajzna a pr\u00c3\u00a1zdn\u00c3\u00a1 n\u00c3\u00a1ru\u00c4\u008d: Major Houlihanov\u00c3\u00a1 hodnot\u00c3\u00ad sv\u00c5\u00afj \u00c5\u00beivot a chce jej zm\u00c4\u009bnit. Rozhodne se rozej\u00c3\u00adt s Frankem a \u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00a1d\u00c3\u00a1 o p\u00c5\u0099elo\u00c5\u00been\u00c3\u00ad. Na rozlu\u00c4\u008dkov\u00c3\u00a9m ve\u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00adrku se opije a kdy\u00c5\u00be zjist\u00c3\u00ad, jak jsou k n\u00c3\u00ad loaj\u00c3\u00a1ln\u00c3\u00ad jej\u00c3\u00ad pod\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adzen\u00c3\u00a9 a kolik m\u00c3\u00a1 vlastn\u00c4\u009b v t\u00c3\u00a1bo\u00c5\u0099e p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00a1tel, sv\u00c3\u00a9 rozhodnut\u00c3\u00ad zm\u00c4\u009bn\u00c3\u00ad.'), NULL),
(9982, '201405/S302.m4v', 'Dark Wings, Dark Words', 4, 1000, 'en', 'cz', 'en', NULL, NULL, 'S302.jpg', 302, 'Dark Wings, Dark Words: Sansa Stark is introduced to Olenna Tyrell and is incautious when questioned about King Joffrey Baratheon. Shae asks Tyrion Lannister for help protecting Sansa. Jaime Lannister provokes Brienne into a duel but finds himself recaptured. Arya Stark crosses paths with the Brotherhood Without Banners and is recognized by their new prisoner Sandor Clegane. Ravens bring dark news to the King in the North at Harrenhal; his brothers are still missing and Hoster Tully has died. Jon Snow learns about wargs from the Free Folk. Bran Stark is surprised to meet new allies in the barren North.', TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:07.126'),
(9973, '201405/S203.m4v', 'What Is Dead May Never Die', 4, 1000, 'en', 'cz', 'en', '', '', 'S203.jpg', 203, 'What Is Dead May Never Die: Catelyn Stark treats with King Renly in the hope of winning an alliance. Tyrion undertakes a complex plan in King''s Landing to expose an enemy. At Winterfell, Bran''s dreams continue to trouble him.', TIMESTAMP '2014-05-29 08:56:06.474'),
(2355, '201309/071 Bile zlato.m4v', 'Bile zlato', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '071 Bile zlato.jpg', 71, STRINGDECODE('N\u00c3\u00a1st\u00c4\u009bnka: Nudu v t\u00c3\u00a1bo\u00c5\u0099e dok\u00c3\u00a1\u00c5\u00bee odstranit jen Henryho pravideln\u00c3\u00a1 p\u00c5\u0099edn\u00c3\u00a1\u00c5\u00a1ka o sexu, p\u00c5\u0099i kter\u00c3\u00a9 Hawkeye s Traperem velmi vyru\u00c5\u00a1uj\u00c3\u00ad. Dal\u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00adm zpest\u00c5\u0099en\u00c3\u00adm \u00c5\u00beivota v t\u00c3\u00a1bo\u00c5\u0099e je film se Shirley Templeovou.'), NULL),
(2310, '201309/027 Radarova zprava.m4v', 'Radarova zprava', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '027 Radarova zprava.jpg', 27, STRINGDECODE('Bombar\u00c4\u008f\u00c3\u00a1k Charlie: Ne\u00c5\u00a1ikovnost severokorejsk\u00c3\u00a9ho pilota, kter\u00c3\u00bd se sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad v\u00c5\u00bedy v 17.00 bombardovat bl\u00c3\u00adzk\u00c3\u00bd sklad st\u00c5\u0099eliva, se stane z\u00c3\u00a1bavou pro cel\u00c3\u00bd t\u00c3\u00a1bor. Frank se sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad prosadit jeho sest\u00c5\u0099elen\u00c3\u00ad, ale d\u00c4\u009blo dostane k dispozici, a\u00c5\u00be kdy\u00c5\u00be Charlie tref\u00c3\u00ad d\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00adp gener\u00c3\u00a1la Claytona. P\u00c5\u0099i v\u00c3\u00bdst\u00c5\u0099elu Frank Charlieho mine a zni\u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00ad inkriminovan\u00c3\u00bd sklad st\u00c5\u0099eliva.'), NULL),
