(2307, '201309/096 Interview.m4v', 'Interview', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '096 Interview.jpg', 96, STRINGDECODE('A\u00c5\u00be t\u00c4\u009b zase uvid\u00c3\u00adm: Hawkeye se setk\u00c3\u00a1v\u00c3\u00a1 se \u00c5\u00beenou, o kter\u00c3\u00a9 si myslel, \u00c5\u00bee ode\u00c5\u00a1la z jeho \u00c5\u00beivota nav\u00c5\u00bedy, ale kterou ve skute\u00c4\u008dnosti nikdy nep\u00c5\u0099estal milovat.'), NULL),
(2312, '201309/029 Dr Pierce a Mr Hyde.m4v', 'Dr Pierce a Mr Hyde', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '029 Dr Pierce a Mr Hyde.jpg', 29, STRINGDECODE('Dr. Pierce a pan Hyde: Hawkeye je 3 dny nep\u00c5\u0099etr\u00c5\u00beit\u00c4\u009b ve slu\u00c5\u00beb\u00c4\u009b a rozhodne se poslat dopis prezidentovi Trumanovi. Pak dostane dal\u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00ad n\u00c3\u00a1pad a ode\u00c5\u00a1le do severn\u00c3\u00ad Koreje latr\u00c3\u00adnu s nab\u00c3\u00addkou k p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adm\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad. Traperovi se nakonec poda\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad jej uklidnit.'), NULL),
(2254, '201309/002 Na trh.m4v', 'Na trh', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '002 Na trh.jpg', 2, STRINGDECODE('Henry, pros\u00c3\u00adm, vra\u00c5\u00a5 se domu: D\u00c3\u00adky \u00c3\u00basp\u00c4\u009bch\u00c5\u00afm jednotky je velitel Henry za odm\u00c4\u009bnu p\u00c5\u0099evelen gener\u00c3\u00a1lem Hammondem na lep\u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00ad m\u00c3\u00adsto do Tokia. Velen\u00c3\u00ad se ujme Frank Burns. Hawkeye a Traper d\u00c4\u009blaj\u00c3\u00ad v\u00c5\u00a1echno pro to, aby p\u00c5\u0099im\u00c4\u009bli Henryho k n\u00c3\u00a1vratu. Vydaj\u00c3\u00ad se do Tokia a po dohod\u00c4\u009b s Radarem p\u00c5\u0099edst\u00c3\u00adraj\u00c3\u00ad, \u00c5\u00bee je mu zle a Henry proto mus\u00c3\u00ad p\u00c5\u0099ijet.'), NULL),
(2313, '201309/030 Kim.m4v', 'Kim', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '030 Kim.jpg', 30, STRINGDECODE('M.D.O. - M\u00c3\u00adstn\u00c3\u00ad domorod\u00c3\u00a1 osoba: Hawkeye, Traper a Radar vyd\u00c3\u00adraj\u00c3\u00ad jednoho poru\u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00adka, aby povolil s\u00c5\u0088atek des\u00c3\u00a1tn\u00c3\u00adka Walkera s m\u00c3\u00adstn\u00c3\u00ad korejskou d\u00c3\u00advkou.'), NULL),
(2304, '201309/093 Smejici se Jack.m4v', 'Smejici se Jack', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '093 Smejici se Jack.jpg', 93, STRINGDECODE('38 rovnob\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u00beka: Ziskuchtiv\u00c3\u00bd Frank se rozhodne v dra\u00c5\u00beb\u00c4\u009b prod\u00c3\u00a1vat Korejc\u00c5\u00afm odpadky z t\u00c3\u00a1borov\u00c3\u00a9 skl\u00c3\u00a1dky, ale nakonec je to Hawkeye, kter\u00c3\u00bd najde jejich vyu\u00c5\u00beit\u00c3\u00ad. Nech\u00c3\u00a1 je shodit z vrtuln\u00c3\u00adku na fanatick\u00c3\u00a9ho plukovn\u00c3\u00adka Coner.'), NULL),
(33610, '201412/TEENAGE_MUTANT_NINJA_TURTLES.m4v', 'Zelvy Ninja', 4, 0, 'cz', 'cz', 'en', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/266800-zelvy-ninja/', 'TEENAGE_MUTANT_NINJA_TURTLES.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Nos\u00ed jm\u00e9na slavn\u00fdch italsk\u00fdch renesan\u010dn\u00edch um\u011blc\u016f, ovl\u00e1daj\u00ed zbran\u011b japonsk\u00fdch ninj\u016f a zbo\u017e\u0148uj\u00ed pizzu. \u017delvy Ninja jsou obrovsk\u00fdm fenom\u00e9nem, kter\u00fd se zrodil p\u0159esn\u011b p\u0159ed t\u0159iceti lety jako \u010dernob\u00edl\u00fd komiks. Producent t\u011b\u017ekoton\u00e1\u017en\u00edch ak\u010dn\u00edch velkofilm\u016f Michael Bay se rozhodl, \u017ee pr\u00e1v\u011b te\u010f nastal \u010das, aby tihle specifi\u010dt\u00ed bojovn\u00edci se zlem opustili str\u00e1nky \u010dasopis\u016f a televizn\u00ed seri\u00e1l a kone\u010dn\u011b s plnou par\u00e1dou vpadli na filmov\u00e9 pl\u00e1tno. Podobn\u011b urputn\u011b Bay kdysi prosazoval prvn\u00ed Transformers, s nimi\u017e vstoupil do elitn\u00edho klubu nej\u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011bj\u0161\u00edch filmov\u00fdch s\u00e1g sou\u010dasnosti. A historie se m\u016f\u017ee opakovat... M\u011bsto New York zoufale pot\u0159ebuje hrdiny. Ovl\u00e1d\u00e1 ho toti\u017e strach a v\u0161ehoschopn\u00fd Trha\u010d, jeho\u017e pozice vl\u00e1dce podsv\u011bt\u00ed je zcela neot\u0159esiteln\u00e1, dokud se v m\u011bstsk\u00e9 kanalizaci vinou nepoda\u0159en\u00e9ho genetick\u00e9ho experimentu neobjev\u00ed \u010dty\u0159i bojovn\u00edci v krun\u00fd\u0159i a s mimo\u0159\u00e1dn\u00fdmi schopnostmi. Tam, kde jsou Michelangelo, Donatello, Leonardo a Raphael, nesm\u00ed pochopiteln\u011b chyb\u011bt ani zv\u011bdav\u00e1 report\u00e9rka April (Megan Fox). Spole\u010dn\u011b odhal\u00ed Trha\u010dovy d\u011bsiv\u00e9 pl\u00e1ny na roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed jeho imp\u00e9ria a rozhodnou se je vlastn\u00edmi v\u00fdrazn\u011b vylep\u0161en\u00fdmi silami p\u0159ekazit.(CinemArt)'), TIMESTAMP '2014-12-26 18:06:18.741');
