(1438, 'SK80/SK80-10 Sladke starosti -- Sweet troubles.m4v', 'Sladke starosti', 18, 0, 'sk', '  ', 'sk', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/4242-sladke-starosti/', 'SK80-10 Sladke starosti -- Sweet troubles.jpg', 50, STRINGDECODE('Kom\u00e9dia o poctivom a \u0161ikovnom cukr\u00e1rovi \u0160imonovi. Skromn\u00fd star\u00fd ml\u00e1denec sa v praktickom \u017eivote st\u00e1va \u013eahkou obe\u0165ou svojho \u0161\u00e9fa, matky a z\u00e1stupu vydajachtiv\u00fdch \u017eien. V pr\u00edbehu sa objavuj\u00fa osved\u010den\u00e9 postupy takmer v\u0161etk\u00fdch d\u00f4le\u017eit\u00fdch obdob\u00ed filmovej kom\u00e9die. Po\u010dn\u00fac lumi\u00e9rovskou etudou so z\u00e1hradnou hadicou cez melancholick\u00e9ho tul\u00e1ka a\u017e po postrach okolia - Jacquesa Tatiho. Jurajovi Herzovi sa tak podarilo v\u00fdrazne obohati\u0165 nielen kolibsk\u00fa dramaturgiu 80. rokov, ale najm\u00e4 skromn\u00fa trad\u00edciu slovenskej kom\u00e9die.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(2279, '201309/052 Laska a svatba.m4v', 'Laska a svatba', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '052 Laska a svatba.jpg', 52, STRINGDECODE('\u00c5\u00bdelez\u00c5\u0088\u00c3\u00a1k Kelly: Gener\u00c3\u00a1l ''\u00c5\u00bdelez\u00c5\u0088\u00c3\u00a1k'' Kelly p\u00c5\u0099ijede na inspekci a nakonec skon\u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00ad v Margaretin\u00c4\u009b stanu. Bohu\u00c5\u00beel, v n\u00c3\u00a1ru\u00c4\u008d\u00c3\u00ad majorky Houlihanov\u00c3\u00a9 ne\u00c4\u008dekan\u00c4\u009b zem\u00c5\u0099e a jeho pobo\u00c4\u008dn\u00c3\u00adk se sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad za\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00addit v\u00c5\u00a1e tak, aby to vypadalo, \u00c5\u00bee gener\u00c3\u00a1l zem\u00c5\u0099el ve velkolep\u00c3\u00a9 bitv\u00c4\u009b. Hawkeye a Traper mu pom\u00c3\u00a1haj\u00c3\u00ad propa\u00c5\u00a1ovat gener\u00c3\u00a1lovo t\u00c4\u009blo z t\u00c3\u00a1bora.'), NULL),
