(1455, 'Lord of the Rings/LOTR-1-FOTR-EXT-CZ-B.m4v', 'Spolecenstvo prstenu, ext, 2', 4, 2, 'cz', NULL, 'en', 'Fellowship of The Ring, ext, 2', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/4711-pan-prstenu-spolecenstvo-prstenu/', 'LOTR-1-FOTR-EXT-CZ-B.jpg', 2, STRINGDECODE('Hlavn\u00edm hrdinou je hobit Frodo Pytl\u00edk, kter\u00fd se ve sv\u00e9 vlastn\u00ed domovin\u011b zvan\u00e9 St\u0159edozem\u011b dostal do samotn\u00e9ho centra bitvy mytick\u00fdch proporc\u00ed. Bude muset b\u011bhem sv\u00e9ho putov\u00e1n\u00ed prok\u00e1zat, \u017ee moc p\u0159\u00e1telstv\u00ed a individu\u00e1ln\u00ed odvahy dok\u00e1\u017ee \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b \u010delit i t\u011bm nejni\u010div\u011bj\u0161\u00edm sil\u00e1m temnoty. Frodova dobrodru\u017estv\u00ed odstartuje dar jeho p\u0159\u00edbuzn\u00e9ho Bilba. Od n\u011bj z\u00edsk\u00e1 magick\u00fd prsten, kter\u00fd Froda postav\u00ed do soboje se silami zla reprezentovan\u00fdmi krutovl\u00e1dcem Sauronem. Ten tou\u017e\u00ed za ka\u017edou cenu z\u00edskat prsten, proto\u017ee je pro n\u011bj zdrojem neomezen\u00e9 moci, jedin\u011b s jeho pomoc\u00ed se mu m\u016f\u017ee poda\u0159it zotro\u010dit lid St\u0159edozem\u011b a st\u00e1t se jeho neomezen\u00fdm p\u00e1nem. Ve snaze \u010delit Sauronov\u00fdm temn\u00fdm pl\u00e1n\u016fm, se mus\u00ed Frodo spojit se n\u011bkolika dal\u0161\u00edmi bytostmi. Vytvo\u0159\u00ed s nimi takzvan\u00e9 Spole\u010denstvo slo\u017een\u00e9 z jeho p\u0159\u00e1tel, \u010darod\u011bje, elfa, trpasl\u00edka a dal\u0161\u00edch pomocn\u00edk\u016f, se kter\u00fdmi se vyd\u00e1 na cestu na jej\u00edm\u017e konci doufaj\u00ed, \u017ee se jim poda\u0159\u00ed prsten jednou prov\u017edy zni\u010dit. Jejich cesta v\u0161ak prok\u00e1\u017ee, \u017ee nejenom magick\u00e9 prsteny, ale tak\u00e9 soun\u00e1le\u017eitost v\u0161ech \u017eiv\u00fdch bytost\u00ed mohou dok\u00e1zat netu\u0161en\u00e9 v\u011bci. Mus\u00ed v\u0161ak \u010delit nejen nebezpe\u010d\u00edm, kter\u00e1 na n\u011b \u010d\u00edhaj\u00ed na \u00fazem\u00edch ovl\u00e1dan\u00fdch Sauronem, ale i rozkladn\u00e9 moci samotn\u00e9ho prstenu.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(1465, 'Lord of the Rings/LOTR-3-ROTK-EXT-EN-B.m4v', 'Return of The King, ext, 2', 4, 2, 'en', 'cz', 'en', NULL, 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0167260/', 'LOTR-3-ROTK-EXT-EN-B.jpg', 12, 'Directed by Peter Jackson.  With Elijah Wood, Viggo Mortensen, Ian McKellen, Orlando Bloom. Gandalf and Aragorn lead the World of Men against Sauron''s army to draw his gaze from Frodo and Sam as they approach Mount Doom with the One Ring.', NULL),
(2275, '201309/023 Primeri.m4v', 'Primeri', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '023 Primeri.jpg', 23, STRINGDECODE('P\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adm\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad: Do t\u00c3\u00a1bora se donese zpr\u00c3\u00a1va od gener\u00c3\u00a1la Claytona, \u00c5\u00bee se chyst\u00c3\u00a1 podpis p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adm\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad. Vypuknou oslavy, Hawkeye je nucen \u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adkat sv\u00c3\u00bdm avant\u00c3\u00bdr\u00c3\u00a1m, \u00c5\u00bee je \u00c5\u00beenat\u00c3\u00bd, odpust\u00c3\u00ad pokerov\u00c3\u00a9 dluhy, jen Traper zpr\u00c3\u00a1v\u00c4\u009b nev\u00c4\u009b\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00ad. Nad\u00c4\u009bje v M*A*S*H pohasnou, kdy\u00c5\u00be doraz\u00c3\u00ad op\u00c4\u009bt nov\u00c3\u00ad zran\u00c4\u009bn\u00c3\u00ad.'), NULL);
