(1580, '201209/Muzi v ciernom -- Men In Black en.m4v', 'Men In Black', 4, 0, 'en', 'cz', 'en', 'Men In Black', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0119654/', 'Muzi v ciernom -- Men In Black en.jpg', NULL, 'Directed by Barry Sonnenfeld.  With Tommy Lee Jones, Will Smith, Linda Fiorentino, Vincent D''Onofrio. A streetwise NYPD detective joins a secret organization that polices extraterrestrial affairs on Earth.', NULL),
(2308, '201309/025 Rozdeleni zustaneme.m4v', 'Rozdeleni zustaneme', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '025 Rozdeleni zustaneme.jpg', 25, STRINGDECODE('Rozd\u00c4\u009bleni z\u00c5\u00afstaneme: Gener\u00c3\u00a1l Clayton po\u00c5\u00a1le psychiatra kpt. Hildebranda na prohl\u00c3\u00addku 4077. Henry \u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00a1d\u00c3\u00a1 osazenstvo, aby se chovali co nejl\u00c3\u00a9pe, nebo budou rozd\u00c4\u009bleni. Marn\u00c4\u009b. Po n\u00c3\u00a1v\u00c5\u00a1t\u00c4\u009bv\u00c4\u009b dr. Hildebrant do zpr\u00c3\u00a1vy nap\u00c3\u00ad\u00c5\u00a1e, \u00c5\u00bee vid\u00c4\u009bl u\u00c4\u008debnicov\u00c3\u00a9 p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adklady neur\u00c3\u00b3z, psych\u00c3\u00b3z, voyerismu, feti\u00c5\u00a1ismu a mnoha dal\u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00adch ism\u00c5\u00af. Bylo by proto \u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00adlen\u00c3\u00a9 tyto lidi od sebe odd\u00c4\u009blit a jejich \u00c5\u00a1\u00c3\u00adlenstv\u00c3\u00ad je\u00c5\u00a1t\u00c4\u009b pos\u00c3\u00adlit.'), NULL),
(2273, '201309/021 Nerozhodne.m4v', 'Nerozhodne', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '021 Nerozhodne.jpg', 21, STRINGDECODE('Nerozhodn\u00c4\u009b: Hawkeye a Frank se h\u00c3\u00a1daj\u00c3\u00ad o Frankov\u00c3\u00bdch chirurgick\u00c3\u00bdch schopnostech (l\u00c3\u00a9pe \u00c5\u0099e\u00c4\u008deno neschopnostech). Jeden z Hawkeyho pacient\u00c5\u00af m\u00c3\u00a1 pot\u00c3\u00ad\u00c5\u00bee a Hawkeye za\u00c4\u008dne pochybovat o sv\u00c3\u00bdch vlastn\u00c3\u00adch schopnostech. Nakonec se uk\u00c3\u00a1\u00c5\u00bee, \u00c5\u00bee chybu ud\u00c4\u009blal Frank.'), NULL),
