(1483, 'Pirati/Pirati z Karibiku - Prokleti cerne perly en.m4v', 'The Curse of the Black Pearl', 15, 26, 'en', 'cz', 'en', '', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0325980/', 'Pirati z Karibiku - Prokleti cerne perly en.jpg', 1, 'Directed by Gore Verbinski.  With Johnny Depp, Geoffrey Rush, Orlando Bloom, Keira Knightley. Blacksmith Will Turner teams up with eccentric pirate "Captain" Jack Sparrow to save his love, the governor''s daughter, from Jack''s former pirate allies, who are now undead.', NULL),
(1484, 'Pirati/Pirati z Karibiku - Truhlica mrtveho muze cz.m4v', 'Truhla mrtveho muze', 15, 26, 'cz', NULL, 'en', 'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man''s Chest', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/194904-pirati-z-karibiku-truhla-mrtveho-muze/', 'Pirati z Karibiku - Truhlica mrtveho muze cz.jpg', 6, STRINGDECODE('Kapit\u00e1n Jack Sparrow (Johnny Depp) zist\u00ed, \u017ee m\u00e1 krvav\u00fa dl\u017eobu u Daveyho Jonesa, kapit\u00e1na lode duchov nazvanej Lietaj\u00faci Holan\u010fan. Ako be\u017e\u00ed \u010das, Jack mus\u00ed n\u00e1js\u0165 sp\u00f4sob ako sa zbavi\u0165 dl\u017eoby, ina\u010d skon\u010d\u00ed prekliaty ve\u010dn\u00fdm prekliat\u00edm. A akoby toho nebolo dos\u0165, Jackove probl\u00e9my ved\u00fa k stroskotaniu svadby Willa Turnera s Elizabeth Swannovou, ktor\u00e9ho Jack nahovor\u00ed aby sa k nemu pripojil na jeho najbli\u017e\u0161ej v\u00fdprave.(sliver)'), NULL),
(1553, '201208/Sin City.m4v', 'Sin City', 15, 0, 'en', NULL, 'en', 'Sin City', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0401792/', 'Sin City.jpg', NULL, 'Directed by Frank Miller, Robert Rodriguez, Quentin Tarantino.  With Mickey Rourke, Clive Owen, Bruce Willis, Jessica Alba. A film that explores the dark and miserable town, Basin City, and tells the story of three different people, all caught up in violent corruption.', NULL),
(1493, '201207/Cesta do fantazie -- Spirited Away.m4v', 'Cesta do fantazie', 3, 0, 'cz', NULL, 'jp', 'Spirited Away', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/42136-cesta-do-fantazie/', 'Cesta do fantazie -- Spirited Away.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Desetilet\u00e1 Chihiro je oby\u010dejn\u00e1 japonsk\u00e1 hol\u010di\u010dka. Kdy\u017e se se sv\u00fdmi rodi\u010di vyd\u00e1v\u00e1 poprv\u00e9 do nov\u00e9ho bydli\u0161t\u011b, jejich auto zabloud\u00ed na opu\u0161t\u011bnou lesn\u00ed cestu, vedouc\u00ed k z\u00e1hadn\u00e9mu tunelu. Chihiro i jej\u00ed rodi\u010de se vydaj\u00ed dovnit\u0159 a objev\u00ed cosi, co pova\u017euj\u00ed za opu\u0161t\u011bn\u00fd lunapark. Rodi\u010de podlehnou l\u00e1kav\u00e9 nab\u00eddce ob\u010derstven\u00ed v opu\u0161t\u011bn\u00fdch st\u00e1nc\u00edch, ale z\u00e1hy se prom\u011bn\u00ed ve vep\u0159e. Chihiro se sna\u017e\u00ed naj\u00edt pomoc a naraz\u00ed na tajupln\u00e9ho chlapce jm\u00e9nem Haku. Ten ji sezn\u00e1m\u00ed s duchy, kte\u0159\u00ed v noci lunapark ob\u00fdvaj\u00ed a najde j\u00ed zam\u011bstn\u00e1n\u00ed u Yubaby, star\u00e9 \u010darod\u011bjnice s mal\u00fdm t\u011blem a velkou hlavou, kter\u00e1 provozuje obrovsk\u00e9 l\u00e1zn\u011b, kam si chod\u00ed odpo\u010dinout mili\u00f3ny pozemsk\u00fdch boh\u016f a jin\u00fdch fantastick\u00fdch bytost\u00ed. Zde se skr\u00fdv\u00e1 jedin\u00e1 mo\u017enost, jak m\u016f\u017ee Chihiro zru\u0161it zaklet\u00ed sv\u00fdch rodi\u010d\u016f a vr\u00e1tit se do lidsk\u00e9ho sv\u011bta.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
