(2309, '201309/026 Charlie o pate.m4v', 'Charlie o pate', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '026 Charlie o pate.jpg', 26, STRINGDECODE('Radarova zpr\u00c3\u00a1va: Radar p\u00c3\u00ad\u00c5\u00a1e t\u00c3\u00bddenn\u00c3\u00ad situa\u00c4\u008dn\u00c3\u00ad zpr\u00c3\u00a1vu - Hawkeye operuje zran\u00c4\u009bn\u00c3\u00a9ho v\u00c4\u009bzn\u00c4\u009b, kter\u00c3\u00bd se zmocn\u00c3\u00ad skalpelu a ohro\u00c5\u00beuje ostatn\u00c3\u00ad, pak se sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad flirtovat s novou sestrou, Frank m\u00c3\u00a1 konflikt s Klingerem, jeho\u00c5\u00be d\u00c3\u00advka doma v USA se chce vd\u00c3\u00a1t, a Henry kv\u00c5\u00afli tomu povol\u00c3\u00a1v\u00c3\u00a1 psychiatra, majora Freedmana.'), NULL),
(1498, '201207/Equilibrium en.m4v', 'Equilibrium', 4, 0, 'en', 'cz', 'en', 'Equilibrium', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0238380/', 'Equilibrium en.jpg', NULL, 'Directed by Kurt Wimmer.  With Christian Bale, Sean Bean, Emily Watson, Taye Diggs. In a Fascist future where all forms of feeling are illegal, a man in charge of enforcing the law rises to overthrow the system.', NULL),
(2323, '201309/040 Zamilovany Henry.m4v', 'Zamilovany Henry', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '040 Zamilovany Henry.jpg', 40, STRINGDECODE('Zamilovan\u00c3\u00bd Henry: Plukovn\u00c3\u00adk Henry se p\u00c5\u0099i dovolen\u00c3\u00a9 v Tokiu zamiluje do dvacetilet\u00c3\u00a9 d\u00c3\u00advky jm\u00c3\u00a9nem Nancy Sue Parkerov\u00c3\u00a1. Hawkeye, Traper a Radar se sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad zaslepen\u00c3\u00a9mu Henrymu zabr\u00c3\u00a1nit ve zni\u00c4\u008den\u00c3\u00ad jeho man\u00c5\u00beelstv\u00c3\u00ad. Nakonec mu naprav\u00c3\u00ad hlavu telefon\u00c3\u00a1t s man\u00c5\u00beelkou.'), NULL),
(1503, '201207/Hudba z Marsu.m4v', 'Hudba z Marsu', 9, 0, 'cz', NULL, 'cz', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/4995-hudba-z-marsu/', 'Hudba z Marsu.jpg', NULL, STRINGDECODE('Zam\u011bstnanci n\u00e1bytk\u00e1\u0159sk\u00e9ho podniku MARS uv\u00edtaj\u00ed vz\u00e1cnou n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvu najatou hudbou. Jejich vychloub\u00e1n\u00ed, jak\u00fd by oni sestavili orchestr, je br\u00e1no v\u00e1\u017en\u011b, proto dostanou mal\u00fd d\u00e1rek - hudebn\u00ed n\u00e1stroje pro t\u0159icet muzikant\u016f.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(2278, '201309/051 Prvni pomoc.m4v', 'Prvni pomoc', 15, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '051 Prvni pomoc.jpg', 51, STRINGDECODE('Jaro: S p\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00adchodem jara dost\u00c3\u00a1v\u00c3\u00a1 Klinger z domova dopis od sv\u00c3\u00a9 snoubenky, \u00c5\u00bee by si jej v Toledu cht\u00c4\u009bla vz\u00c3\u00adt. Otec Mulcahy (s Radarovou pomoci) za\u00c5\u0099\u00c3\u00add\u00c3\u00ad svatbu pomoc\u00c3\u00ad kr\u00c3\u00a1tkovln\u00c3\u00a9ho r\u00c3\u00a1dia. Radar se zamiluje do sestry, mezit\u00c3\u00adm vd\u00c4\u009b\u00c4\u008dn\u00c3\u00bd pacient nechce Hawkeyho nechat samotn\u00c3\u00a9ho a neust\u00c3\u00a1le se mu sna\u00c5\u00be\u00c3\u00ad pom\u00c3\u00a1hat. Prost\u00c4\u009b p\u00c5\u0099i\u00c5\u00a1lo jaro.'), NULL),
