(2000, '201301/Dark Knight Rises en.m4v', 'Dark Knight Rises', 15, 27, 'en', 'cz', 'en', 'Dark Knight Rises', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1345836/', 'Dark Knight Rises en.jpg', 12, 'Directed by Christopher Nolan. With Christian Bale, Tom Hardy, Anne Hathaway, Gary Oldman. Eight years on, a new terrorist leader, Bane, overwhelms Gotham&#x27;s finest, and the Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.', NULL),
