(2387, '201312-2/ST_NEMESIS.m4v', 'Nemesis', 4, 38, 'en', 'cz', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0253754/?ref_=fn_al_tt_2', 'ST_NEMESIS.jpg', 10, 'Directed by Stuart Baird.  With Patrick Stewart, Jonathan Frakes, Brent Spiner, LeVar Burton. After the Enterprise is diverted to the Romulan planet of Romulus, supposedly because they want to negotiate a truce, the Federation soon find out the Romulans are planning an attack on Earth.', NULL),
