(841, 'Rychle a Zbesile.m4v', 'Rychle a Zbesile', 15, 37, 'en', '  ', 'en', 'The Fast And The Furious', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/1616-rychle-a-zbesile/', 'Rychle a Zbesile.jpg', 1, STRINGDECODE('Brianovi se kone\u010dn\u011b poda\u0159\u00ed st\u00e1t se \u010dlenem party veden\u00e9 Dominicem, kter\u00fd je doslova bl\u00e1zen do neleg\u00e1ln\u00edch z\u00e1vod\u016f, po\u0159\u00e1dan\u00fdch v\u011bt\u0161inou v noci na perif\u00e9rii Los Angeles. Je to obrovsk\u00e9 divadlo pro obecenstvo zb\u011bsil\u00fdch j\u00edzd, ale p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm posedlost pro piloty speci\u00e1ln\u011b upraven\u00fdch superau\u0165\u00e1k\u016f. S ohlu\u0161uj\u00edc\u00edm \u0159evem motor\u016f, \u0159\u00edt\u00edc\u00ed se m\u011bstem n\u011bkolikan\u00e1sobkem povolen\u00e9 rychlosti, p\u011bn\u00ed v\u0161em adrenalin v krvi. Ve h\u0159e jsou pen\u00edze, presti\u017e, obdiv d\u00edvek. Jen\u017ee pro Dominica a jeho k\u00e1mo\u0161e nejsou z\u00e1vody jedin\u00fdm zdrojem financ\u00ed. A to je hlavn\u00ed d\u016fvod, pro\u010d chce policista Brian z\u00edskat jeho d\u016fv\u011bru. V posledn\u00ed dob\u011b se mno\u017e\u00ed z\u00e1hadn\u00e1 p\u0159epaden\u00ed kamion\u016f a policie i FBI cht\u011bj\u00ed zn\u00e1t pachatele d\u0159\u00edv ne\u017e tir\u00e1ci vezmou z\u00e1kon do sv\u00fdch rukou. Ve chv\u00edli, kdy m\u00e1 v\u0161echny d\u016fkazy o tom, \u017ee Dominic je v\u016fdcem gangu, Brian zav\u00e1h\u00e1 s odhalen\u00edm pravdy. Zamiloval se do jeho sestry Miy a je mu jasn\u00e9, \u017ee j\u00ed t\u00edm zp\u016fsob\u00ed dvojn\u00e1sobn\u00fd \u0161ok. Mia nev\u00ed, \u010d\u00edm se ve skute\u010dnosti bratr \u017eiv\u00ed, ani netu\u0161\u00ed, kdo vlastn\u011b Brian je...(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(2375, '201312-2/A_I_ARTIFICIAL_INTELLIGENCE.m4v', 'Artificial Intelligence: A.I.', 4, 0, 'en', NULL, 'cz', NULL, 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0212720/?ref_=nv_sr_1', 'A_I_ARTIFICIAL_INTELLIGENCE.jpg', NULL, 'Directed by Steven Spielberg.  With Haley Joel Osment, Jude Law, Frances O''Connor, Sam Robards. A highly advanced robotic boy longs to become "real" so that he can regain the love of his human mother.', NULL),
