(1444, 'Batman/Batman 1 Begins-cz.m4v', 'Batman zacina', 15, 27, 'cz', NULL, 'en', 'Batman Begins', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/136224-batman-zacina/', 'Batman 1 Begins-cz.jpg', 1, STRINGDECODE('Film popisuje po\u010d\u00e1tky legendy o tajemn\u00e9m Batmanovi a zjeven\u00ed Temn\u00e9ho ryt\u00ed\u0159e coby s\u00edly dobra v Gotham City. Zklaman\u00fd d\u011bdic tov\u00e1ren Bruce Wayne cestuje t\u011bsn\u011b po \u00famrt\u00ed sv\u00fdch rodi\u010d\u016f po sv\u011bt\u011b a hled\u00e1 zp\u016fsob, jak\u00fdm by bojoval s nespravedlnost\u00ed a jak by obr\u00e1til strach proti t\u011bm, kte\u0159\u00ed okr\u00e1daj\u00ed b\u00e1zliv\u00e9. Po \u010dase se vrac\u00ed zp\u011bt do Gotham City a vz\u00e1p\u011bt\u00ed vypou\u0161t\u00ed do sv\u011bta sv\u00e9 druh\u00e9 j\u00e1, maskovan\u00e9ho bojovn\u00edka Batmana, kter\u00fd pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 svoji s\u00edlu, inteligenci a \u0159adu sv\u00fdch technick\u00fdch vymo\u017eenost\u00ed k boji proti zlov\u011bstn\u00fdm sil\u00e1m, kter\u00e9 ohro\u017euj\u00ed m\u011bsto...(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL);
