(1523, '201208/Americka krasa -- American Beauty en-en.m4v', 'American Beauty', 15, 0, 'en', 'en', 'en', 'American Beauty', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0169547/', 'Americka krasa -- American Beauty en-en.jpg', NULL, 'Directed by Sam Mendes.  With Kevin Spacey, Annette Bening, Thora Birch, Wes Bentley. Lester Burnham, a depressed suburban father in a mid-life crisis, decides to turn his hectic life around after developing an infatuation for his daughter''s attractive friend.', NULL),
