(859, 'Twin Peaks.m4v', 'Twin Peaks', 15, NULL, 'cz', '  ', 'en', 'Twin Peaks: Fire Walk With Me', 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/6260-twin-peaks/', 'Twin Peaks.jpg', 140, STRINGDECODE('Teresa Banksov\u00e1 byla zavra\u017ed\u011bna. Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed agent FBI, kter\u00fd zlo\u010din vy\u0161et\u0159oval, zmizel beze stopy. Agent Cooper se marn\u011b sna\u017e\u00ed rozmotat p\u0159\u00edpad, obest\u0159en\u00fd rou\u0161kou z\u00e1had a tajemstv\u00ed. Jedin\u00fdm v\u00fdsledkem jeho sna\u017een\u00ed je neodbytn\u00fd pocit, \u017ee nezn\u00e1m\u00fd vrah za\u00fato\u010d\u00ed znovu. Uplyne rok. Ocit\u00e1me se v m\u011bste\u010dku Twin Peaks. Pod rou\u0161kou poklidn\u00e9 st\u0159edostavovsk\u00e9 idyly buj\u00ed s\u00edly temnot a vl\u00e1dne strach. Nevinn\u00e9 tv\u00e1\u0159e n\u011bkter\u00fdch st\u0159edo\u0161kola\u010dek skr\u00fdvaj\u00ed n\u00e1vyk na kokain a neuspo\u0159\u00e1dan\u00fd sexu\u00e1ln\u00ed \u017eivot. Jedn\u00e9 z nich, Lau\u0159e, zb\u00fdv\u00e1 posledn\u00edch sedm dn\u00ed \u017eivota...(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
