(1398, 'SK60/SK60-01 Janosik I.m4v', 'Janosik I', 18, 0, 'sk', '  ', 'sk', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/84727-janosik-i-ii/', 'SK60-01 Janosik I.jpg', 11, STRINGDECODE('Nesmrteln\u00e1 legenda o zbojnick\u00e9m hrdinovi J\u00e1no\u0161\u00edkovi, kter\u00fd bohat\u00fdm bral a chud\u00fdm d\u00e1val, je st\u00e1le vd\u011b\u010dn\u00fdm n\u00e1m\u011btem r\u016fzn\u00fdch um\u011bleck\u00fdch zpracov\u00e1n\u00ed. T\u0159et\u00ed filmov\u00e1 verze, kter\u00e1 byla nato\u010dena na Kolib\u011b v letech 1962-63, vznikla u p\u0159\u00edle\u017eitosti 250. v\u00fdro\u010d\u00ed J\u00e1no\u0161\u00edkovy smrti. N\u00e1m\u011bt, sc\u00e9n\u00e1\u0159 i re\u017eie t\u00e9to velkolep\u00e9 historick\u00e9 fresky jsou d\u00edlem Palo Bielika - p\u016fvodn\u00edho hereck\u00e9ho p\u0159edstavitele J\u00e1no\u0161\u00edka z \u010desk\u00e9 Fri\u010dovy filmov\u00e9 verze z roku 1935. Zaj\u00edmav\u00e9 je, \u017ee hlavn\u00ed roli nesv\u011b\u0159il zku\u0161en\u00fd herec \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9mu z herc\u016f, ale mlad\u00e9mu l\u00e9ka\u0159i z I\u013eavy, Franti\u0161ku Kuchtovi. Neokoukan\u00e1 tv\u00e1\u0159 tak vtiskla cel\u00e9mu filmov\u00e9mu vypr\u00e1v\u011bn\u00ed siln\u00fd, realistick\u00fd n\u00e1dech. Velkorys\u00fd projekt, nat\u00e1\u010den\u00fd v exteri\u00e9rech slovensk\u00fdch hor, s velkou \u00fa\u010dast\u00ed komparsu, n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fdmi sc\u00e9nick\u00fdmi stavbami (d\u016fmysln\u00e1 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed J\u00e1no\u0161\u00edkova l\u00e1gera) a s \u00fa\u010dast\u00ed plej\u00e1dy vynikaj\u00edc\u00edch slovensk\u00fdch herc\u016f, pat\u0159\u00ed k poklad\u016fm slovensk\u00e9 kinematografi.(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL),
(1408, 'SK60/SK60-11 Skalni v ofsajde -- Soccer Fans.m4v', 'Skalni v ofsajde', 18, 0, 'sk', '  ', 'sk', NULL, 'http://www.csfd.cz/film/28165-skalni-v-ofsajde/', 'SK60-11 Skalni v ofsajde -- Soccer Fans.jpg', 21, STRINGDECODE('Komedi\u00e1lne laden\u00fd pr\u00edbeh o troch priate\u013eoch, \"skaln\u00fdch fan\u00fa\u0161ikoch\", ktor\u00ed sa sna\u017eia z\u00edska\u0165 vstupenky na v\u00fdznamn\u00fd futbalov\u00fd z\u00e1pas s braz\u00edlskym klubom. V\u0161etci pracuj\u00fa v projektovom \u00fastave a robia v\u0161etko preto, aby mohli povzbudi\u0165 svoje mu\u017estvo na chystanom z\u00e1pase. Len\u017ee v\u0161etko sa im vymyk\u00e1 z r\u00fak...(ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed text distributora)'), NULL);
